\subsubsection parameters ROS parameters

Reads and maintains the following parameters on the ROS server

- \b "~kp" : \b [double] Proportional gain. min: 0.0, default: 1.4, max: 10.0
- \b "~ki" : \b [double] Integral gain. min: 0.0, default: 0.0, max: 10.0
- \b "~kd" : \b [double] Derivative gain. min: 0.0, default: 0.1, max: 10.0
- \b "~speed" : \b [double] Vehicle speed (m/s). min: 0.0, default: 0.0, max: 7.0

